original_title: Queens: Parsons Boulevard - Grand Central Parkway
text:
Parsons Boulevard (foreground), at the N.W. corner of Grand Central Parkway, showing an old homestead. The house and a 50-acre farm was owned by J. Lott in 1873. Phoebe Ely owned the property in 1909. View 2 shows Grand Central Parkway under construction. Lott Lane formerly ran here.

P. L. Sperr

View 1: March 27, 1927
View 2: March 25, 1932
